room_title: Escape room "Forgotten Pharaoh" by Escape This Madison in Madison
room_description: You’re among a team of archaeologists who’ve set out to unravel the mysteries surrounding a long-forgotten Pharaoh whose identity to this day, remains unknown. Drawn by rumors of treasure and unimaginable wealth, you also know that all who have come before you have inexplicably disappeared. Do you have the skills - and the guts! - to make the discovery of a lifetime and escape to tell about it?
